link: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 9..1000
formula: a(n) ~ log(10) * exp(Pi*sqrt(3*n/5)) / (2 * Pi * 15^(1/4) * n^(1/4)). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Oct 25 2018
